---
---
<section class="py-12 md:py-16" style="background: var(--brand-navy);">
  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 md:gap-12 items-center">

    <!-- Left: copy (mobile: order 2) -->
    <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--brand-cta-accessible); margin-bottom: 12px;">
        Why Men Choose Us
      </p>
      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px); color: var(--c-text-on-dark); line-height: 1.1; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Your labs might be normal.<br />You still don't feel right.
      </h2>

      <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 20px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); font-family: var(--font-body);">
        Most men wait two years before saying something out loud. They get bloodwork. Their GP says everything looks fine. They go home. Nothing changes.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); font-family: var(--font-body);">
        We specialize in men's health. One licensed provider, your labs, and a real conversation. Not a coordinator reading from a tablet. A real, in-person conversation about how you actually feel. If treatment is right for you, you leave with a plan the same day.
      </p>

      <!-- Blockquote -->
      <figure style="border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.35); box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.10); margin-top: 28px; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; position: relative; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);">
        <svg aria-hidden="true" style="position: absolute; top: -14px; left: 16px; height: 40px; width: 40px; color: var(--brand-cta); opacity: 0.90;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/></svg>
        <blockquote style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: italic; margin-top: 8px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92); font-family: var(--font-body);">
          "Saw two GPs who told me my levels were fine. I knew they weren't. Three weeks after starting treatment I was sleeping through the night again. The difference in energy over the next few months was something no standard lab panel ever captured."
        </blockquote>
        <figcaption style="margin-top: 12px; font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); font-family: var(--font-body);">
          <span>James T., 48, Norfolk</span>
          <span style="display: block; margin-top: 4px; font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.50);">Verified member. Individual results vary.</span>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <a
        href="#hero-form"
        onclick="event.preventDefault(); document.getElementById('hero-form')?.scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'});"
        style="margin-top: 28px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; font-weight: 700; border: none; height: 56px; min-height: 56px; background: var(--brand-cta); color: var(--c-text-on-dark); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; font-family: var(--font-display); text-transform: uppercase; white-space: nowrap; border-radius: 60px; padding: 0 32px; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer;"
      >
        Book in-person visit
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
      <p style="margin-top: 12px; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); font-family: var(--font-body);">
        No-obligation in-person visit. Individual results vary.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: image (mobile: order 1) -->
    <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
      <img
        src="/images/patient-trt.webp"
        alt="Phlebotomist drawing labs for a Virginia man at a Men's Wellness Center"
        class="rounded-2xl w-full"
        style="aspect-ratio: 4/3; object-fit: cover; object-position: center 35%; box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,0.40);"
        width="600"
        height="450"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
